        <definition>uint8_t bt_le_adv_param::id</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>id</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_le_adv_param::id</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Local identity handle. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The index of the identity address in the local Bluetooth controller.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>When extended advertising <computeroutput>CONFIG_BT_EXT_ADV</computeroutput> is not enabled or not supported by the controller it is not possible to scan and advertise simultaneously using two different random addresses. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
