        <name>sid</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_le_adv_param::sid</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Advertising Set Identifier, valid range is <ref refid="group__bt__gap__defines_1gacf05b7660d2ae85f64e2a220abf8e57d" kindref="member">BT_GAP_SID_MIN</ref> to <ref refid="group__bt__gap__defines_1gafa6f803fe3ada07030fb1f2f725940c4" kindref="member">BT_GAP_SID_MAX</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Requires <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1ggafbf81dab68b0e484d4742471c722fc28ae33ae9d8e43cce82e47fa73999d415ab" kindref="member">BT_LE_ADV_OPT_EXT_ADV</ref> bit (see <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1gafbf81dab68b0e484d4742471c722fc28" kindref="member">bt_le_adv_opt</ref> field) to be set as <ref refid="structbt__le__adv__param_1a2a978c60153eb03697769bc72928f4ef" kindref="member">bt_le_adv_param::options</ref>. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
